</p>
<p>Let's experiment and see what that does! Go back and just run <code>gulp</code>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">gulp</div></code></pre>
<p>Ok, it dumps out <code>undefined</code>. Now run it with <code>--production</code>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">gulp --production</div></code></pre>
<p>Hey, it's <code>true</code>! Ok, one step closer. </p>
<p>Let's add a new config value called <code>production</code> and set that to <code>!!util.env.production</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="228a0dc263">
